    pitching            :   +28.1 runs  ++++++++++++++
    positional          :    +0.0 runs  
    TOTAL               :   +43.5 runs

  WHY BRAVS DIVERGES:
  Rivera's 1.38 ERA in 78 IP is excellent but limited volume.
